          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the Social Justice &amp; Empowerment Department website: [https://esamajkalyan.gujarat.gov.in](https://esamajkalyan.gujarat.gov.in/index.aspx)\n**Step 2:** Click on “Please Register Here” on the homepage.\n**Step 3:** Fill in your personal details as per Aadhaar.\n**Step 4:** Create a password and submit the form.\n**Step 5:** Verify details and click “Confirm”.\n**Step 6:** You will receive your User ID &amp; Password via SMS/email.\n> **Login Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Go to the portal homepage.\n**Step 2:** Enter your User ID, Password, and Captcha.\n**Step 3:** Click “Login” to access your dashboard.\n> **Application Process:**\n\nAfter login, complete your User Profile (first-time only).\n**Step 1:** Homepage will show eligible schemes – click on the one you want.\n**Step 2:** Fill out the scheme application form.\n**Step 3:** Upload the required documents.\n**Step 4:** Review all entries, agree to terms, and click “Save Application”.\n**Step 5:** Note your Application Number for tracking.\n> **Track Application:**\n\n**Step 1:** Click on “[View Application Status](https://esamajkalyan.gujarat.gov.in/ViewApplicationStatus.aspx)”.\n**Step 2:** Enter your Application Number and Date of Birth.\n**Step 3:** Click “View Status” to check progress.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
